volunteering, Armando--

00:06:52.490 --> 00:06:55.010 align:middle line:84%
is it's hard to
describe in words

00:06:55.010 --> 00:06:58.700 align:middle line:84%
or even remember the details
of the financial accounts.

00:06:58.700 --> 00:07:02.540 align:middle line:84%
We started in the lecture
