00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:12.140 align:middle line:84%
And then we added and subtracted
across the various line items

00:07:12.140 --> 00:07:14.910 align:middle line:84%
to produce what
we called product.

00:07:14.910 --> 00:07:16.835 align:middle line:84%
So you can go back
and review that.

00:07:16.835 --> 00:07:20.510 align:middle line:90%


